<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Banff Trail</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Established in 1952, the Banff Trail Real Estate is very popular for its unique ‘Motel
                Village’ that comprises a bevy of 20 motels and hotels located along the Crowchild Trail. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Banff Trail comprises of single-family detached homes, apartment
                condominiums and a few recently developed infills that are readily available at an average price of
                $760,000. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">Among the several recreational venues located in the neighborhood, the Confederation Park,
                McMahon Stadium, and the Jubilee Auditorium are most notable for their popularity among the locals.</p>


